魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我既諗法係 我覺得有方法可以代替到果個人<br />\n令佢真正鍾意我<br />\n正如你溝一條女之前，條女都唔一定鍾意你啦"},{"pid":"ad08e1a18464021deb87fe1c11fd21327c27c377","tid":17612,"uid":50265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手就好<br />\n巴打幾多歲？<br />\n佢浪費左你一年既時間，向前看啦好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n廿歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔係浪費既，呢一年過得真係好開心<br />\n其實佢同我分手都唔係岩岩 都有一個月 所以我都睇開左<br />\n不過係諗唔通點解姐"},{"pid":"8c42e6c03122b4a88dca33eac1af61ed96335a23","tid":17612,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:41:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da171bcde3fe9be81f6cf54a8e20c39bb23e9f9d","tid":17612,"uid":48984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"女人就係會花心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打takecare"},{"pid":"61c023bbaa58bf6eedfd9f42c22dae4c8a8c9fba","tid":17612,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"下個更可愛"},{"pid":"e0586c5b92066d462902a13138228c0fdba4d6b8","tid":17612,"uid":50265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係咁同女友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過中意另一個嘅人係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\noh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解咁做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n控制唔到自已中意嗰個人<br />\n好努力避開都成日諗住<br />\n唔通仲繼續同女友一齊但心中諗第二個咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.